6) Rules (Money Bin invariants)

1. Reversibility

Compressed → must expand back without loss of intent

2. Anchors

Always define core terms before compressing

3. Layer separation

Definition ≠ Narrative ≠ Compression

4. No fake mysticism

“Feels deep” ≠ “is precise”


